==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zythum
<hw>Zy"thum</hw> <pr>(z⟦icr⟧"th⟦ucr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
fr. Gr. <grk>zy^qos</grk> a kind of beer; -- so called by the
Egyptians.]</ety> <def>A kind of ancient malt beverage; a liquor made
from malt and wheat.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>zythem</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

